data.description: Charming 3 bed 2 bath one story located in the desirable Bliss Meadows neighborhood. This home features beautiful hardwood floors throughout most of the home. Brick gas or log burning fireplace in living room. Nice size primary bedroom with walk in closet and built in shelving. Extended deck in the back yard with newly redone cover.  AC and water heater replaced in 2020. Roof was repaired due to storm/missing shingles. The new shingles do not match yet no issues at all with leaks. Schedule your appointment for viewing today!
